ViridianLake_Text_Trainer_Tips:
	.string "TRAINER TIPS\p"
	.string "In thick FOG, accuracy drops; moves\n"
	.string "like AERIAL ACE and SHOCK WAVE never\p"
	.string "miss, so keep them handy if you want\n"
	.string "to find your way and win battles!$"

